data.text:
Palo Premium supplement pages are fully illustrated in color! Pages include spaces for all major stamps issued during the year and are laid out in the same order as the Scott catalog - catalog numbers are not included. Available in regular (without mounts) or hingeless (with mounts) - hingeless pages require a 2 to 4 week lead time. Black & white pages are available upon request.

Cream-colored, 100 lb. acid-free paper

Page dimensions: 10 ¾" x 12 ¼" (275mm x 310mm)

Fits exclusively in Palo Premium 5-ring binders

Binder Label

$1.50

Palo binder labels are customized to your specifications. Country names, collection years, volumes, topical titles and more - organize and display your perfect collection! Please specify label content at checkout. NOTE: If you order consists only of labels, please call us to place your order.

Black with gold lettering for black binders

Clear with white lettering for red, green and blue binders

2” x ¾” (50mm x 19mm)

Premium Binder with Slipcase

$88.50

Palo Premium binders complete your collection. Specifically made to fit Palo Premium pages, this 5-ring binder holds pages firmly in place while allowing them to lay completely flat - it's also extremely easy to add or remove pages. Manufactured in leatherette or genuine leather and includes a matching slipcase. Approximately 100 pages fit in each binder.

Leatherette available in black, blue, red or green (binder/slipcase shades may vary)

Genuine leather available in black only

Black binders have gold detailing on spine and black metal corners; blue/red/green binders have white detailing on spine and nickel metal corners

Comes with page lifters and black covers

Binder with slipcase dimensions: 12¼" x 13⅛" x 2 ¼"
